@IRULE010: copy, or drag the key file to "c:\program files\winrar" folder

There are 2 ways:

Start WinRAR and drag the rarreg.key into the window. WinRAR automatically places the file in the winRAR folder.

Or you can manually copy rarreg.key to the WinRAR folder.

In most cases the WinRAR folder is:
C:\Program Files\WinRAR\
